    <item>
      <title>TikTok 剥离或禁止法案即将在美国国会快速通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-moving-on-fast-track-through-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据众议院议长迈克·约翰逊周三概述的一项计划，迫使 TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动有限公司剥离其社交媒体平台所有权的努力将很快成为法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-moving-on-fast-track-through-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:26:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚大学校长因教授赞扬哈马斯而受到立法者拷问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/columbia-s-president-grilled-over-professors-who-praised-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚大学校长米努什·沙菲克 (Minouche Shafik) 受到包括埃莉斯·斯特凡尼克 (Elise Stefanik) 在内的立法者的压力，要求解释为什么 10 月 7 日赞扬哈马斯行动的教授仍然是教职人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/columbia-s-president-grilled-over-professors-who-praised-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:10:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗地亚总理普伦科维奇在激烈的选举中遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/croatia-s-plenkovic-may-lose-majority-in-vote-exit-polls-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚总理安德烈·普连科维奇在紧张的全国选举中遭遇挫折，因为他面临总统佐兰·米拉诺维奇的挑战，后者嘲笑对乌克兰的军事援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/croatia-s-plenkovic-may-lose-majority-in-vote-exit-polls-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国为加沙寻求25亿美元，比之前多十倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/israel-hamas-war-un-seeks-2-5-billion-for-gaza-humanitarian-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国正在寻求25亿美元的资金，用于今年剩余时间内对加沙的人道主义援助，这一数额比六个月前呈指数级增长，这突显了陷入以色列-哈马斯战争的人们的处境日益恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/israel-hamas-war-un-seeks-2-5-billion-for-gaza-humanitarian-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将恢复对委内瑞拉的制裁，声称马杜罗破坏了协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在确定尼古拉斯·马杜罗政权未能履行允许在定于 7 月举行的选举中进行更公平投票的协议后，总统乔·拜登政府重新对委内瑞拉实施石油制裁，结束了六个月的缓期执行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织称中美债务给全球公共财政带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/imf-says-us-china-debt-pose-risks-for-global-public-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织(IMF)官员表示，世界两大经济竞争对手中国和美国将在未来五年内推动全球公共债务的增长，而美国的支出通过维持高利率给许多其他国家带来麻烦。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/imf-says-us-china-debt-pose-risks-for-global-public-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保费上涨，保险公司称诉讼是罪魁祸首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/insurers-blame-higher-premiums-on-lawsuits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“社会通货膨胀”是他们用来描述他们所认为的滥用法律制度的术语。支持者表示，几乎没有证据表明两者之间存在联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/insurers-blame-higher-premiums-on-lawsuits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登告诉钢铁工人，美国钢铁公司“保证”仍为美国所有</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/higher-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-aluminum-sought-by-biden-in-2024-election-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登誓言要让美国钢铁公司继续由美国控股，并呼吁对中国钢铁和铝征收更高的关税，因为他试图在 11 月大选前争取工会工人的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/higher-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-aluminum-sought-by-biden-in-2024-election-push</guid>
